nodes.title: Meeting Notes - Project Planning
nodes.start_anchor: Meeting Notes - Project Planning: This meeting focused on planning the upcoming project phases and allocating resources.
nodes.end_anchor: The meeting concluded with a clear action plan and assigned responsibilities for the next phase of the project.

nodes.title: Agenda Items
nodes.start_anchor: Agenda Items: The meeting agenda included several key topics that needed to be addressed.
nodes.end_anchor: All agenda items were successfully addressed during the meeting with clear outcomes and next steps identified.

nodes.start_anchor: Budget Discussion: The team reviewed the current budget allocation and identified areas where additional funding might be required.
nodes.end_anchor: The budget discussion resulted in a revised allocation that better reflects the project's current needs and constraints.

nodes.title: Action Items
nodes.start_anchor: Action Items: Several action items were identified during the meeting that require immediate attention.
nodes.end_anchor: All action items have been documented and will be tracked through the project management system.

nodes.title: Next Steps
nodes.start_anchor: Next Steps: The team outlined the immediate next steps that need to be taken to move the project forward.
nodes.end_anchor: The next steps have been prioritized and scheduled to ensure timely completion of all project milestones.
